Text: <c.white><c.mono_sans>This is no way to treat guests,</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Well, I can tell you at once,</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and I want it returned to me.</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Every piece of land has a price,</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>so he can put to King Horik</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and I will say no more now!</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Who is she, anyway, to put such</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>One day he was fine, and the</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>made him sweat and cry out in</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>then it must be the same tree</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>he is the only one in Kattegat</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and the start of your own fame?</c.mono_sans></c.white>
